headline: Consumers Energy, Michigan State University Celebrate Partnership to Power Next Generation of Graduates
summary: Consumers Energy and Michigan State University are celebrating a partnership and $250,000 in financial support that is powering the next generation of college graduates to stay and work in Michigan.
